Not sure where to post this. There is a typo in the documentation of <https://developers.HubSpot.com/docs/cms/guides/email/hubdb-crm-objects>.
In the custom object example the ~ is placed within the ” which causes an error. I’m pretty sure it should be this:

```{% set query = "price__lte="~contact.budget_max~"&amp;price__gte="~contact.budget_min~"&amp;city="~contact.city~"&amp;order=listing_name" %}
{% set real_estate_listings = crm_objects("p2990812_Property", query, "listing_name, location, price, address, type") %}
{% for home in real_estate_listings.results %}

...

{% endfor %}```
